              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Only a fraction do, organically. LinkedIn's algorithm prioritises posts from individual profiles over Company Pages, which typically reach 2-5% of followers organically. To reach more followers, invest in employee advocacy (employees sharing company posts) or use LinkedIn Ads to boost high-performing organic content.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

